Etchika Choureau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Etchika_Choureau 0 Etchika Choureau (born 19 November 1929) is a French film actress. She was at one point in a relationship with Hassan II of Morocco, who was then heir to the throne. Etchika_Choureau ( born 19_November_1929 ) is a_French_film_actress .
